I"<p>Three laws of objects. Sounds catchy enough? To me, it did. I read about these laws in <a href="https://amzn.to/2VoCO0k">Ken Pugh’s Prefactoring</a>.</p>

<p>If you sense a not too much-hidden reference to Asimov’s <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Three_Laws_of_Robotics">Three Laws of Robotics</a> from <a href="https://amzn.to/2Rp2sD8">I, Robot</a>, it’s not a coincidence. It’s the author’s purpose.</p>

